# Firmware-only devshell — Rust + flip-link + probe-rs etc.,
# no Node / pnpm. Activates when you `cd firmware/rmk`.
#
# Reads the ROOT flake (../../flake.nix, two levels up). No
# per-subdirectory flake exists — kobu has exactly one source of truth
# at the repo root. `watch_file` makes direnv reload this shell whenever
# the root flake or its lockfile changes, so bumping Rust or any other
# dependency at the root invalidates the firmware cache too.
watch_file ../../flake.nix ../../flake.lock
use flake "path:../..#firmware"
